#: enterprise_catalog/apps/catalog/models.py:685
msgid ""
"The UUID that represents a piece of content. This value is usually a "
"secondary identifier to content_key in the enterprise environment."
msgstr ""
"UUID inayowakilisha kipande cha maudhui. Thamani hii kawaida ni kitambulisho"
" cha pili cha content_key katika mazingira ya kampuni."

#: enterprise_catalog/apps/catalog/models.py:695
#: enterprise_catalog/apps/catalog/models.py:840
msgid ""
"The key that represents a piece of content, such as a course, course run, or"
" program."
msgstr ""
"Ufunguo unaowakilisha kipande cha maudhui, kama vile kozi, ratiba ya kozi, "
"au programu."

#: enterprise_catalog/apps/catalog/models.py:710
msgid ""
"The key represents this content's parent. For example for course_runs "
"content their parent course key."
msgstr ""
"Ufunguo unaowakilisha mzazi wa maudhui haya. Kwa mfano, kwa maudhui ya "
"course_runs, ni ufunguo wa kozi ya mzazi."

#: enterprise_catalog/apps/catalog/models.py:721
msgid ""
"The metadata about a particular piece content as retrieved from the "
"discovery service's search/all endpoint results, specified as a JSON object."
msgstr ""
"Metadata kuhusu kipande fulani cha maudhui kama ilivyopatikana kutoka kwa "
"matokeo ya huduma ya utambuzi (search/all endpoint), iliyopangwa kama kitu "
"cha JSON."

